    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span><br>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Sekali setiap Ronde</span>: jika di Tanganmu tidak terdapat <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Seats Scared and Secular</span>, maka menciptakan kartu <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Seats Scared and Secular</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/08/15595270/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_6164844579465035716.png",
                "id": "talent55502",
                "key": "Soloist's Solicitation",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Soloist's Solicitation"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Saat ini <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Furina</span> berada dalam status Arkhe: Ousia: memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Salon Members</span>.</p><p>(Saat Furina berada dalam status Arkhe: Pneuma, memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Singer of Many Waters</span>)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/47e3b8a03c0e9406c19655e1aa7c3b30_5917990319331940745.png",
                "id": "talent54935",
                "key": "Salon Solitaire",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Salon Solitaire"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Universal Revelry</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Universal Revelry</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Setelah Karakter aktifmu menerima DMG atau pemulihan: </span>menambah 1 poin<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Revelry</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Durasi (Ronde): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/e5d9f5e8170236ccfb246be6a8bee57f_3973517113412704282.png",
                "id": "talent99002",
                "key": "Let the People Rejoice",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Let the People Rejoice"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] Menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Seats Sacred and Secular</span> di Tanganmu saat duel dimulai.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/be37947534ecad684025e9577469afa4_1686107329355250997.png",
                "id": "talent85001",
                "key": "Arkhe: Seat Sacred and Secular",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Arkhe: Seat Sacred and Secular"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Kartu Peristiwa</span></p><p>Saat berada di status Arkhe: Pneuma atau Arkhe: Ousia, ganti status Furina.</p><p>Jika kamu memiliki <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Salon Members</span> atau <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Singer of Many Waters</span> di arena, ubah juga statusnya.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7613226546747713624.png",
                "id": "talent23234",
                "key": "Seats Sacred and Secular",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/b4812801014e3b4dfaed86c27639933c_5313630694386045664.png",
                "title": "Seats Sacred and Secular"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. Jika kamu memiliki Karakter dengan minimum 6 poin HP, maka mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> kepada Karaktermu yang menerima DMG paling sedikit, lalu mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span> (Dapat ditumpuk hingga 4 lapis)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8969392474324395442.png",
                "id": "talent97230",
                "key": "Salon Members",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/742ece024b8fa2d5c64bdb5a98710fb7_115378360680832274.png",
                "title": "Salon Members"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> memulihkan 1 poin HP seluruh Karaktermu.  Jika kamu memiliki Karakter yang HP-nya tidak lebih dari 5 poin, maka memulihkan lagi 1 poin HP Karakter yang telah menerima DMG terbanyak.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 2</span> (Dapat ditumpuk hingga 4 lapis)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8646455993149362881.png",
                "id": "talent90949",
                "key": "Singer of Many Waters",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/d87cb48ac9ce6214f901cfb7aa5cc542_3585739070207419910.png",
                "title": "Singer of Many Waters"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Hydro dan memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan sebuah [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] yang memberikan +2 poin DMG untuk kasus Pyro/Electro DMG-mu selanjutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_1040662734706264162.png",
                "id": "talent52075",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Revelry</span></strong><br>Karaktermu mengakibatkan DMG +1. (Termasuk DMG Swirl yang dipicu Karakter) </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Jumlah Penggunaan: 1</span> (Dapat ditumpuk tanpa batas)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG tidak dapat dipengaruhi oleh Bonus DMG apa pun, namun tidak dapat ditahan oleh efek seperti Perisai atau kekebalan DMG.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span></strong></p><p>Setiap kali kamu mencapai Tahap Selesai di setiap Ronde, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> -1.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durasi (Ronde)</span> habis.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/01/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1762013092009813397.png",
                "id": "talent43127",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
